name: df-2ndf
params: setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3, setvar s4
body: |- wceq(c2ndf, cmpo(s0, s1, ccat, ccat, csb(s2, cxp(cfv(cbs, cv(s0)), cfv(cbs, cv(s1))), cop(cres(c2nd, cv(s2)), cmpo(s3, s4, cv(s2), cv(s2), cres(c2nd, co(cv(s3), cfv(chom, co(cv(s0), cxpc, cv(s1))), cv(s4))))))))
comment: Define the second projection functor out of the product of categories. (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 11-Jan-2017.)
